Application to generate Christmas shapes

Usage:
  bin/shapesGenerator [options]

Options:
  --size[=size] Oprional. Size of Christmas shapes. Possible values: S, M, L. Default is random size

Examples:
  bin/shapesGenerator
  bin/shapesGenerator --size=M

To use web version of application you need to start built-in PHP web server
  php -S localhost:9000 -t ./web/
And then open http://localhost:9000 page in browser for random shapes OR http://localhost:9000?size=<shapeSize> to generate specific size shapes